Rating: 4
An excellent main dish for a special evening. We had "A Night in Morocco" with several guests, and this recipe is worth the time and effort. The sauce was a bit viscous when boiled down, but scrumptious nonetheless. We did vary it a bit; we grilled the marinated hens instead of baking. A nice alternative.